A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a vast neon-lit warehouse filled with towering shelves of glowing software packages and data cubes, each emitting different colored lights in electric blues, magentas, and cyans. A lone figure in a hooded jacket stands at a holographic terminal in the center, streams of light connecting from various shelves to their workstation like luminous threads. The architecture features exposed circuitry patterns on the walls, rain-slicked metallic floors reflecting the ambient glow, and distant rows of repositories fading into a misty purple haze. Floating holographic icons drift through the air like digital fireflies, representing different applications waiting to be collected and installed.
